<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="subscribe-vi">subscribe <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /səb'skraɪb/    美 /səb'skraɪb/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>订阅 (报纸、杂志等)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>subscribe to</strong> Time 
订阅《时代》周刊</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>定期交纳 (会费)；定期捐款：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>subscribe to</strong> a charity 
向慈善机构定期捐款</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="subscribe-to">subscribe to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[正式用语] 同意；赞成：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>All scientists subscribe to the view that the increase in the earth’s temperature is due to the burning of fossil fuels.
所有的科学家都赞成这种观点：地球上气温的升高是由燃烧矿物燃料引起的。</p><footer>人教⑥ – 4</footer></div></div>